{"tid":1391602,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 國軍來了我帶路","createTime":"2019-07-31T13:17:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T13:31:08.000Z","uid":109701,"like":3,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"cd7a84bd839def3283c2379ed89a6e477313c015","tid":1391602,"uid":109701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:17:03.000Z","msg":"大家一定好想<span style=\"color: red;\">sir</span>係必要時候嚟香港幫手 但係基於無名無實 出師無名 名不正言不順 sir都好難主動開口嚟幫拖<br />\n<br />\n小弟認為 如果想sir可以光明正大嚟助陣 就要先借中華民國嘅名義 請求<span style=\"color: red;\">國軍嚟香港</span>幫助香港嘅中華同胞<br />\n<br />\n如果可以令到台灣嚟幫手 咁就可以令sir以<span style=\"color: red;\">美台關係</span>嘅名義 嚟香港幫手打大boss<br />\n<br />\n可能係天方夜譚 如有錯 請屌<br />\n<br />\n有得諗=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66587a4a4fffe24da6afeb8a0efcbf90cdb26abd","tid":1391602,"uid":109701,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:18:22.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"77c9f8de5de58fde1803b421d79fd82dea7478b1","tid":1391602,"uid":109701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:18:34.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"e3f2ba89b0469914449691490bfa5e312175ffbb","tid":1391602,"uid":109701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:18:48.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"6ed18a12e35a5d3764aa86d4aad4852d947343d9","tid":1391602,"uid":109701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:19:00.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"d892b37a3c8793436938c278e3b20cb38aafff00","tid":1391602,"uid":109701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-31T13:19:10.000Z","msg":"#我係香港人 <br />\n#我會參與8月5日三罷 <br />\n#罷工罷市罷課"},{"pid":"9d8d7dfb389793fd6bab6b077da18f7c9dc